[
    {
        "text": "Hello, I am\nGuillermo del Toro.",
        "start": 0.54,
        "duration": 1.8
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m the director\nof Nightmare Alley.",
        "start": 2.34,
        "duration": 2.78
    },
    {
        "text": "[APPLAUSE]",
        "start": 5.12,
        "duration": 1.76
    },
    {
        "text": "The scene we’re looking at\nis the first time we see",
        "start": 6.88,
        "duration": 3.09
    },
    {
        "text": "the show of mentalism and\nclairvoyance that Stanton",
        "start": 9.97,
        "duration": 4.65
    },
    {
        "text": "Carlisle, the central\ncharacter of the film,",
        "start": 14.62,
        "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
        "text": "played by Bradley\nCooper, is doing.",
        "start": 17.38,
        "duration": 2.52
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s the first time we’re\nseeing him in his new persona",
        "start": 19.9,
        "duration": 3.15
    },
    {
        "text": "with a tuxedo and a\nbandage with an eye,",
        "start": 23.05,
        "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
        "text": "which is a symbol that\nis recurrent in the film.",
        "start": 25.93,
        "duration": 3.01
    },
    {
        "text": "And he is going to meet\nthe main female antagonist,",
        "start": 28.94,
        "duration": 5.57
    },
    {
        "text": "Lilith Ritter, played\nby Cate Blanchett.",
        "start": 34.51,
        "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
        "text": "And we have Stanton\ndoing the show, which",
        "start": 37.39,
        "duration": 3.72
    },
    {
        "text": "is a word code divination\nshow with Rooney Mara, who",
        "start": 41.11,
        "duration": 5.52
    },
    {
        "text": "plays Molly.",
        "start": 46.63,
        "duration": 1.38
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m using the searchlights and\nthe cabaret act to backlight",
        "start": 48.01,
        "duration": 4.53
    },
    {
        "text": "them.",
        "start": 52.54,
        "duration": 0.75
    },
    {
        "text": "When I introduce Lilith,\nthe camera singles her,",
        "start": 53.29,
        "duration": 3.99
    },
    {
        "text": "and we see her backlit\nby this searchlight.",
        "start": 57.28,
        "duration": 2.46
    },
    {
        "text": "So these searchlights\nare used often just",
        "start": 59.74,
        "duration": 3.63
    },
    {
        "text": "to underline a\nmoment between them.",
        "start": 63.37,
        "duration": 2.31
    },
    {
        "text": "The location is shaped\nin the form of a circle",
        "start": 65.68,
        "duration": 2.73
    },
    {
        "text": "because circles start pursuing\nStanton from the first time",
        "start": 68.41,
        "duration": 4.95
    },
    {
        "text": "he sees the geek show,\na horrible sideshow",
        "start": 73.36,
        "duration": 3.99
    },
    {
        "text": "in a carnival.",
        "start": 77.35,
        "duration": 1.59
    },
    {
        "text": "And that is a character that\neats chickens and snakes,",
        "start": 78.94,
        "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
        "text": "and he does it in\na circular pit.",
        "start": 82.54,
        "duration": 2.55
    },
    {
        "text": "And, from that\nmoment on, Stanton",
        "start": 85.09,
        "duration": 2.46
    },
    {
        "text": "is surrounded by\ncircles in the film.",
        "start": 87.55,
        "duration": 3.23
    },
    {
        "text": "“Concentrate.",
        "start": 90.78,
        "duration": 0.85
    },
    {
        "text": "Do any other details\ncome to you?”",
        "start": 91.63,
        "duration": 2.91
    },
    {
        "text": "“There is an inscription.",
        "start": 94.54,
        "duration": 2.54
    },
    {
        "text": "Letters.",
        "start": 97.08,
        "duration": 0.58
    },
    {
        "text": "Am I correct?”",
        "start": 97.66,
        "duration": 1.575
    },
    {
        "text": "“You are.”",
        "start": 99.235,
        "duration": 0.889
    },
    {
        "text": "[APPLAUSE]",
        "start": 100.124,
        "duration": 1.966
    },
    {
        "text": "And it’s an environment in\nwhich he is out of his depth,",
        "start": 102.09,
        "duration": 3.9
    },
    {
        "text": "but he doesn’t know it yet.",
        "start": 105.99,
        "duration": 2.097
    },
    {
        "text": "“Yes, please give\nme the object.”",
        "start": 108.087,
        "duration": 1.375
    },
    {
        "text": "“No, thank you.",
        "start": 109.462,
        "duration": 1.388
    },
    {
        "text": "I’ll hold it.”",
        "start": 110.85,
        "duration": 1.065
    },
    {
        "text": "“Very well.”",
        "start": 111.915,
        "duration": 2.34
    },
    {
        "text": "“Master Stanton, what is the\nobject being held by this",
        "start": 114.255,
        "duration": 2.775
    },
    {
        "text": "lady?”",
        "start": 117.03,
        "duration": 5.668
    },
    {
        "text": "“Well, it seems it’s\na night of gold.",
        "start": 122.698,
        "duration": 1.542
    },
    {
        "text": "A golden handbag.”",
        "start": 124.24,
        "duration": 1.44
    },
    {
        "text": "[APPLAUSE]",
        "start": 125.68,
        "duration": 2.63
    },
    {
        "text": "“Be quiet, child.",
        "start": 128.31,
        "duration": 2.329
    },
    {
        "text": "Let me ask the questions.",
        "start": 130.639,
        "duration": 3.751
    },
    {
        "text": "What is inside the bag?”",
        "start": 134.39,
        "duration": 6.135
    },
    {
        "text": "“Madam, what is the\nmeaning of this?”",
        "start": 140.525,
        "duration": 3.925
    },
    {
        "text": "“You say you’re genuine, and\nI say you use verbal signals",
        "start": 144.45,
        "duration": 3.54
    },
    {
        "text": "of some sort to communicate\nbetween the two of you.”",
        "start": 147.99,
        "duration": 3.345
    },
    {
        "text": "Stanton is not without\ntalent, and this scene",
        "start": 151.335,
        "duration": 3.285
    },
    {
        "text": "becomes a duel between\nhim and the way",
        "start": 154.62,
        "duration": 3.54
    },
    {
        "text": "she sees him and\nhim trying to prove",
        "start": 158.16,
        "duration": 3.54
    },
    {
        "text": "that he is superior to\neveryone, including herself.",
        "start": 161.7,
        "duration": 3.87
    },
    {
        "text": "When we started staging\nthe first few scenes",
        "start": 165.57,
        "duration": 2.82
    },
    {
        "text": "between Bradley\nand Cate, I tried",
        "start": 168.39,
        "duration": 3.78
    },
    {
        "text": "to get them not\nto be equidistant.",
        "start": 172.17,
        "duration": 3.84
    },
    {
        "text": "I wanted Bradley\nto move around.",
        "start": 176.01,
        "duration": 2.43
    },
    {
        "text": "Both here and when he\nvisits her in her office,",
        "start": 178.44,
        "duration": 2.715
    },
    {
        "text": "it is basically two tigers\ncircling each other.",
        "start": 181.155,
        "duration": 4.095
    },
    {
        "text": "So I had Bradley do a whole\ncircuit on that circle",
        "start": 185.25,
        "duration": 4.17
    },
    {
        "text": "and come to her and take\na couple of steps down.",
        "start": 189.42,
        "duration": 5.64
    },
    {
        "text": "“A small pistol.”",
        "start": 195.06,
        "duration": 0.75
    },
    {
        "text": "[AUDIENCE GASPS]",
        "start": 195.81,
        "duration": 2.33
    },
    {
        "text": "“Nickle plated.",
        "start": 198.14,
        "duration": 0.72
    },
    {
        "text": "Ivory handle.",
        "start": 198.86,
        "duration": 3.105
    },
    {
        "text": "May I?”",
        "start": 201.965,
        "duration": 2.415
    },
    {
        "text": "And it’s both a match\nand a seduction.",
        "start": 204.38,
        "duration": 4.83
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s really a ritual and a\nduel that I’m trying to set",
        "start": 209.21,
        "duration": 4.71
    },
    {
        "text": "up, both.",
        "start": 213.92,
        "duration": 0.89
    },
    {
        "text": "[APPLAUSE]",
        "start": 214.81,
        "duration": 3.05
    }
]